summary: An ordinance approving and confirming the assessment and assessment roll of Local Improvement District No. 5125 for the improvement of the alleys in Block "C" Kinnear Park Addition, being the Alleys in the Block between 3rd Avenue West and 4th Avenue West, and between West Mercer Street and West Roy Street; by paving and otherwise improving the same; under Ordinance No. 59090, and levying and assessing the amounts thereof against the several lots, tracts, parcels of land and other property as shown on said roll, establishing a Local Improvement Fund.
